About this app

No matter how far, Traveloka will always be by heart. Discover more than 20 travel products at the tip of your finger with Southeast Asia’s leading travel platform and unravel the world, your way!

Improve your travel experience with our user-friendly travel app, available in English, Indonesian, Malay, Thai, and Vietnamese.

Seamlessly book transportation, accommodation, or local attractions, and pay conveniently using Traveloka PayLater, credit cards, bank transfers, or other various payment methods.

Every day, Traveloka offers the best deal price for transportation and accommodation booking. It’s time to pack your bag and install the Traveloka app.

FIND THE BEST FLIGHT PROMO EVERY DAY

- More than 100,000 flight routes
- Book cheap flight tickets
- Choose from a wide range of reputable airlines, including Singapore Airlines, Scoot, Jetstar, AirAsia, Malaysia Airlines, Emirates, Etihad, Qatar Airways, and other international airlines

TRAVEL WITH DIVERSE GROUND TRANSPORTATION

- Book Traveloka Car Rental with or without driver to your desired destinations and departure points
- Find and book the best deal on train tickets
- Numerous destinations and routes with Bus & Shuttle

BOOK HOTEL AND VARIOUS TYPES OF ACCOMMODATION

- Convenient hotel booking in one app
- More than 100,000 hotels worldwide
- Wide range of hotel options, from budget hotels to 5-star hotels
- Pay Upon Check-In option available

DISCOVER ACTIVITIES WITH TRAVELOKA XPERIENCE

- Never a dull moment with us, find and book tickets to various activities for your trip with Traveloka Xperience
- Activate location to receive specially-curated recommendations of nearby activities
- Ongoing best-deal Xperience promos are always here for you

REFUND & RESCHEDULE WITHIN SECONDS

- Book hotels and flights with no worries
- Traveloka Flexibility features accommodate any last-minute changes in your travel plan
- Reschedule and refund flights, hotels, and train tickets with no worries

BE A PART OF TRAVELOKA PRIORITY

- Become a part of Traveloka Priority member and enjoy exclusive benefits
- Collect Priority Points from every transaction on the Traveloka App
- Higher Priority status unlocks more rewards, discounts, and benefits

ADVANCED FEATURES IN ONE APP

- Fill in the booking form quickly with Passenger Quick-Pick
- Monitor cheap flight ticket with the Price Alert feature
- Save your favorite places and products in the Save List
- Enjoy last-minute bookings for a spontaneous trip

SEE THE WORLD THROUGH TRAVELOKA EXPLORE

- Traveloka Explore is a travel content-sharing platform within the Traveloka app
- Browse through hotel recommendations, fun things to do, and other travel inspirations uploaded by other globetrotters
- Share your trip experience by uploading your own content

24-HOUR MULTILINGUAL CUSTOMER SERVICE

- Round-the-clock, available 24/7
- Quick responses and assistance from the customer service team
- Multilingual customer service team fluent in English, Indonesian, Malay, Thai, and Vietnamese
- Available to assist via phone, chat, or email
- Intelligent Virtual Assistant (IVAN) accessible through the in-app chat feature

AWARD WINNING TRAVEL PLATFORM

Over the past 11 years, Traveloka has been honored with several awards, which prove our dedication to making travel easier through technology.

- TOP Brand Awards 2023: Online Flight and Travel Booking Site, and Online Hotel Reservation Site
- WOW Brand 2023: Gold for Best Online Travel Agents in Indonesia
- Campaign Asia 2023: Top 50 Brands in Customer Experience
- FutureCFO Excellence Awards 2023: Technology Innovation - Most Innovative Use of Automation
- Best National Champion 2022 by Indonesian Ministry of State-Owned Enterprises: Distributor category from the Private sector

Find more inspirations and the latest deals via Instagram, Facebook, and Twitter @traveloka
